  "title": "Common Mistakes and How to Fix Them",
  "lessonText": "Learn to identify and correct common strumming mistakes.",
  "data": {
    "content": "- Strumming too hard: Use a lighter touch for better control.\n- Inconsistent rhythm: Practice with a metronome to improve timing.\n- Missing strings: Focus on your strumming angle and hand position.\n- Overthinking: Relax and let your hand move naturally.\n- Not listening: Record yourself to hear areas for improvement."
  }
}
